summary: Pilot Plant Work Request (PPLW) is a request for a pilot plant to be grown in a controlled environment. The plant will be able to grow a variety of plants at different stages of development. PILOT PLANT WORK REQUEST includes a set of samples for pilot plants and a list of plant types.
